s offer only once;##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>Please take it, or despair.'##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>&nbsp;##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>The fly thought hard upon his ex-##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>istential situation##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>While spider drooled, venom pooled,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>In … mmm… an…ti…ci…   pation.##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>&nbsp;##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>At last he found his courage,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>And spoke unto webspinner,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>'There isn't that much I can say,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>If you must have your dinner,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>&nbsp;##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>But since your dinner's half of me,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>And I can't use the rest,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>I find your offer interesting,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>But for me, it's not what's best.##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>&nbsp;##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>I've called in all my friends, you see,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>I've cashed in I.O.U.s.##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>I've activated protocols,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>So mind your Ps and Qs.'##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>&nbsp;##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>A cloud of black blocked out the sun,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>As flies flocked to his aid.##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>'My friends have come to rescue me,'##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>He wished and hoped and prayed.##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>&nbsp;##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>'How generous you are, my friend!',##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>Said spider to his guest,##/li>			##li class='poem welcome line'>'I only thought to invite one